# Catch The Blocks Game

## Team Members
- Ayaaz Khan I
- Sriharshini S
- Dhanish Kumar V
- Roja Munilakshmi S

## Game Description
Catch The Blocks is a browser-based interactive game where players must click highlighted blocks to earn points. Missing too many blocks ends the game.

## How to Play
- Click the Start button to begin
- Click the green blocks when they appear
- Each correct click earns 10 points
- Missing 5 blocks ends the game

## Key Features
- Start, Play, and Game Over states
- Live score tracking
- Interactive grid-based UI
- Restart functionality

## Programming Concepts Used
- Variables and data types
- Conditional statements
- Loops and nested loops
- Functions
- Arrays
- DOM manipulation
- Event handling

